Package com.ee364project

Class Solution

java.lang.Object
com.ee364project.Solution
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class Solution extends Object implements Cloneable
The ConversationData class encapsulates data related to conversations between customers and agents in a simulated environment. It includes randomization functionality and arrays for customer and agent dialogue intros and responses. Fields:
  • random: A Random instance used for generating random values.
  • customerIntro: An array containing possible introduction phrases from customers.
  • customerResponses: An array containing possible responses from customers.
  • agentIntro: An array containing possible introduction phrases from agents.
  • agentResponses: An array containing possible responses from agents.
Author:
Team 2
